name: HUSTLE ↔ BUSTLE (Those Busy Streets)
description: The daily drudge takes us all. Sometimes it's better if you're only the observer. To what end does our life's work amount to if it weren't for the living to pass them down by choice. Time is indefatigable—a metaphysical construct far from our realm of understanding. And yet, with it's unrelenting, impressive march through the cosmos, we continue to have the audacity to challenge this eternal presence.
